“We at Aon believe that talent is the foundation of successful business operations,” he said. “We’ve been honored by many, but this recognition is a testament to our ability to help clients bring their global talent into New York. From the initial assessment of candidate suitability to the development, management, and delivery of the talent, we’ve seen successful outcomes from our clients, and we continue to do so.”
